{
  "stem": "95.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And then somehow somebody remembered my sister Elaine, and said she was deported two weeks ago.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "Now, in Drancy, people stayed-- it depends, if they stayed maybe a week, two weeks, a month.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Some stayed longer.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "Some stayed overnight.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And that's what happened with our case.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "I mean, they woke us up the next morning.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "Now, I was arrested on the 24th. 24th, I was-- 24th I was in Drancy.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "The 25th in the morning, at 3 o'clock in the morning, they woke us up with a list of people who will be deported that day.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And there we were.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And on the list, there were my mother, and my father, my married sister Ida, with her husband and two young.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "Sons, who escaped where they were living.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "They were living in the 20th arrondissement.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "They escaped that-- that place because they were supposed to be arrested on July 16th, and thought they were going to be safe with us.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And from July 16th until September 23rd, they lived with us, and they were arrested with us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And then my uncle and I were on that list.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "There's a remarkable man called Serge Klarsfeld.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "Serge Klarsfeld, like his wife Beate-- who's not Jewish, but she might as well be.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "She's a saint compared to a lot of Jews-- they are Nazi hunters, like Simon Wiesenthal.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "And Serge, who has lost his father in Auschwitz, made a vow to himself, if he survived, I'm going to see to it that nobody will forget about the Holocaust.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "He got hold of the records in France, because, again, Hitler wanted a thousand-year Reich.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "He wanted to conquer the world.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "He wanted to tell the-- the non-Jews, look what I'm doing to you-- a thousand-year Reich, no Jews, no minorities.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
